data.description: Cozy and bright move-in ready home in Salt Lake City. This 4 bed/1.5 bath home boasts a recently remodeled kitchen and updated full bath, easy flowing floor plan, large sunny windows, and a refresh of paint and flooring throughout. With a 2-car garage, covered carport, and roomy driveway, there is plenty of parking and storage options for all seasons. The spacious0.18 acre yard features a generously-sized poured patio and is fully fenced in both the front andback yards- perfect for relaxation and safe play. Conveniently located with close proximity to the airport, schools, downtown Salt Lake, and more! Its easy access to both I-215 and I-80 makes your commute to dining, shopping, and entertainment, work, and travela breeze!Perfect as a full time residence or as an income producing investment property.
